are you in a relationship with your ex-manager?

281
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:51,200
I think we should talk about the movie first.

282
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:54,930
We've strayed way off topic.

283
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:57,420
Oops! All right then.

284
00:20:57,420 --> 00:21:01,850
I will let you talk about the movie you're promoting today.

285
00:21:01,850 --> 00:21:03,450
Please.

286
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:08,960
So the guy in this picture is you. Right?

287
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:18,870
Right. That's me.

288
00:21:18,870 --> 00:21:21,630
I'm sorry...

289
00:21:21,630 --> 00:21:23,800
That's why you were gone.

290
00:21:23,800 --> 00:21:25,800
You were seeing him.

291
00:21:25,800 --> 00:21:27,920
Why didn't you tell me then?

292
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:31,040
Wait. Aren't you mad at me?

293
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:33,780
Why would I be?

294
00:21:33,780 --> 00:21:36,760
Whoever Puen is seeing is his personal business.

295
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:39,848
I'm his fan, not the master of his life.

296
00:21:43,850 --> 00:21:45,764
Thank you.

297
00:21:46,410 --> 00:21:49,170
Thank you for your understanding.

298
00:21:49,170 --> 00:21:51,060
But I'm a shipper.

299
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:56,416
How is it though?

300
00:21:57,450 --> 00:21:59,480
Normal.

301
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:02,580
You're not acting normal.

302
00:22:04,170 --> 00:22:07,680
No. I'm always like this.

303
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,580
Isn't that hot?

304
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:16,452
You're turning red.

305
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,440
Who are you calling?

306
00:22:34,170 --> 00:22:35,600
Talay.

307
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:37,150
You can't.

308
00:22:37,150 --> 00:22:41,636
I don't know what the relationship between you and Talay is.

309
00:22:41,636 --> 00:22:45,424
But you're being watched by the media.

310
00:22:45,424 --> 00:22:49,150
So contacting Talay is prohibited.

311
00:22:49,150 --> 00:22:52,212
It's affecting your movie.

312
00:22:55,370 --> 00:23:00,490
Prikyuak, at least let me talk to him for a second.

313
00:23:00,490 --> 00:23:02,810
I talked to the management team.

314
00:23:02,810 --> 00:23:07,028
Your phone will be in my care for a while.

315
00:23:07,797 --> 00:23:10,970
Do not contact anyone until the news dies out.

316
00:23:10,970 --> 00:23:13,180
I'm sorry about this.

317
00:23:44,460 --> 00:23:46,712
Will he be okay?

318
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:36,772
[One week later]

319
00:25:02,190 --> 00:25:03,363
Go ahead.

320
00:25:03,363 --> 00:25:05,263
Thank you.

321
00:25:10,810 --> 00:25:12,410
Up!

322
00:25:18,336 --> 00:25:19,950
My name is Tup.

323
00:25:19,950 --> 00:25:23,653
I'm from an editing team. You mistook me for someone else.

324
00:25:25,280 --> 00:25:27,300
I'm sorry.

325
00:25:27,300 --> 00:25:29,270
Tup!

326
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:32,040
Did you get the snack I told you to grab?

327
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:35,000
I'm so hungry I could eat a keyboard.

328
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:37,120
Keep it down, Tou.

329
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:39,376
You don't have to speak so loud.

330
00:25:39,376 --> 00:25:41,076
Here.

331
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:49,463
You were about to grab one. Here.

332
00:25:50,928 --> 00:25:53,300
- Thank you.
- Sure.

333
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:08,160
Nothing.

334
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:10,767
Someone I know loves this so much.

335
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,850
Thank you, Up.

336
00:26:13,850 --> 00:26:15,750
It's Tup.

337
00:26:16,290 --> 00:26:17,690
Jomtup.

338
00:26:17,690 --> 00:26:20,330
Ah, Jomtup.

339
00:26:20,330 --> 00:26:22,620
Yes, I'm Jomtup.

340
00:26:24,117 --> 00:26:25,720
Damn.

341
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:28,764
Multiverse is so damn chaotic.

342
00:26:29,710 --> 00:26:33,210
Are you guys close?

343
00:26:33,210 --> 00:26:35,010
That's right.

344
00:26:35,850 --> 00:26:38,920
This is Tou from the editing team as well.

345
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:41,320
We joined around the same time.

346
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:45,400
Wait.

347
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:47,316
Are you Talay?

348
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:49,630
Yes.

349
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:53,977
Do you two know me?

350
00:26:53,977 --> 00:26:55,550
Of course, we do.

351
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:59,572
The news about you and Puen dating is all over the place.

352
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,043
About that...

353
00:27:07,043 --> 00:27:08,810
It's all good.

354
00:27:08,810 --> 00:27:11,420
We kind of figured it out.

355
00:27:11,420 --> 00:27:14,724
Puen is pretty obvious about it.

356
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,860
How?

357
00:27:18,860 --> 00:27:23,460
A while ago, Puen came here asking for you every day.

358
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:28,960
Excuse me. Is there any employee named Talay here?

359
00:27:38,090 --> 00:27:42,440
We could see it in his eyes he's so in love.

360
00:27:43,290 --> 00:27:46,852
Tou, don't tease him.

361
00:27:47,560 --> 00:27:50,000
It's okay, Talay.

362
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,300
We won't tell anyone.

363
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:54,432
You can trust us.

364
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:59,140
We get what you need to go through dating someone famous.

365
00:27:59,140 --> 00:28:02,587
But hang in there. We're rooting for you, man.

366
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,140
Thank you.

367
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:14,880
Are you Talay?

368
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,860
May we get an interview?

369
00:28:16,860 --> 00:28:19,100
- Please answer some questions.
- I...

370
00:28:19,100 --> 00:28:21,870
Are you the guy in that picture with Puen?

371
00:28:21,870 --> 00:28:23,968
Are you?

372
00:28:23,968 --> 00:28:25,798
Is that right?

373
00:28:25,798 --> 00:28:29,740
I am. The guy in that picture is me.

374
00:28:29,740 --> 00:28:33,650
Did Puen really kiss you on the cheek?

375
00:28:33,650 --> 00:28:36,430
He did.

376
00:28:36,430 --> 00:28:38,778
Are they dating?

377
00:28:38,778 --> 00:28:44,464
But it was just two old colleagues playing with each other.

378
00:28:45,652 --> 00:28:51,270
I confirm here Puen and I...

379
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:54,360
are just two good friends.

380
00:28:54,360 --> 00:28:56,380
Will you excuse me?

381
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:58,160
- Please wait a minute.
- Excuse me, Talay.

382
00:28:58,160 --> 00:29:02,716
So he just made it clear they're only friends.

383
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:15,100
Why did you say that to the press?

384
00:29:15,100 --> 00:29:17,508
Don't you love Puen anymore?

385
00:29:18,010 --> 00:29:22,320
I love him. That's why I said it.

386
00:29:22,320 --> 00:29:26,160
Would you let someone you love lose his job

387
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:28,710
because of you?

388
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:36,480
I get you. But what are you going to do now?

389
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:38,400
Nothing.

390
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:41,736
Going our separate ways is a good way out.

391
00:29:58,080 --> 00:30:00,280
- Puen.
- Hold on, girl.

392
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:02,160
Puen is filming a show today.

393
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,820
No fans assembling here.

394
00:30:03,820 --> 00:30:06,380
He will see you at the next open event. Okay?

395
00:30:06,380 --> 00:30:10,000
But this is a present from me. Can you please accept it?

396
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:13,150
- But it's a private event...
- Prikyuak.

397
00:30:13,150 --> 00:30:15,350
It's okay.

398
00:30:15,350 --> 00:30:17,470
- Thank you.
- Thanks, honey.

399
00:30:17,470 --> 00:30:20,924
Next time, come to an open event.

400
00:30:20,924 --> 00:30:23,628
You must open it.

401
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,250
We have more fans waiting.

402
00:30:28,250 --> 00:30:32,030
These kids. I told them it was a private event today and yet they came.

403
00:30:32,030 --> 00:30:33,310
Ready, Puen?

404
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:38,750
The question is if you face the same situation as the guy in the movie,

405
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:40,110
what would you choose?

406
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:43,004
Work or love?

407
00:31:03,180 --> 00:31:05,388
There you are.

408
00:31:10,410 --> 00:31:12,736
Hey, I've got something to ask you.

409
00:31:12,736 --> 00:31:16,330
Mountain and sea, what will you choose?

410
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:20,380
Sea, of course. My name answers it all.

411
00:31:20,380 --> 00:31:23,820
What about white and pink?

412
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:27,299
No doubt. Pink.

413
00:31:28,490 --> 00:31:31,060
Your smile is so sweet.

414
00:31:34,250 --> 00:31:37,530
My turn to ask you.

415
00:31:37,530 --> 00:31:39,230
Shoot.

416
00:31:40,460 --> 00:31:45,930
Between work and love,

417
00:31:45,930 --> 00:31:47,850
what will you choose?

418
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:53,420
Love, of course.

419
00:31:53,420 --> 00:31:55,290
No.

420
00:31:55,290 --> 00:31:57,290
I'm serious here.

421
00:31:59,530 --> 00:32:04,192
Without your job, you won't have money.

422
00:32:05,120 --> 00:32:07,580
Without money,

423
00:32:08,620 --> 00:32:11,676
it's hard to take care of the one you love.

424
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:18,672
I'll let you answer again.

425
00:32:20,120 --> 00:32:22,460
What will you choose?

426
00:32:22,460 --> 00:32:23,610
For me, I choose...

427
00:32:23,610 --> 00:32:26,448
Excuse me. Sorry to interrupt.

428
00:32:26,448 --> 00:32:29,120
Just a second, please.

429
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:30,620
Puen,

430
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:33,890
have you seen this?

431
00:32:33,890 --> 00:32:35,693
He did kiss my cheek.

432
00:32:35,693 --> 00:32:41,447
But it was just two old colleagues playing with each other.

433
00:32:42,531 --> 00:32:48,100
I confirm here that Puen and I

434
00:32:48,100 --> 00:32:50,810
are just two good friends.

435
00:33:01,050 --> 00:33:02,580
Puen,

436
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:05,980
seriously.

437
00:33:05,980 --> 00:33:08,024
Are you and Talay a thing?

438
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:11,710
Not just a thing.

439
00:33:11,710 --> 00:33:14,590
We're way more connected than that.

440
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:18,444
But you know well what showbiz is like, Puen.

441
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:22,640
I don't want to butt in.

442
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:26,180
But just forget about it.

443
00:33:27,050 --> 00:33:28,940
Please.

444
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:31,624
It's good that you two are apart.

445
00:33:34,460 --> 00:33:37,820
These are the presents from your fans.

446
00:33:37,820 --> 00:33:39,740
Don't open them yet. Go to bed.

447
00:33:39,740 --> 00:33:41,530
Take a good rest.

448
00:33:41,530 --> 00:33:44,450
You will answer the press about Talay in the morning.

449
00:33:45,207 --> 00:33:47,731
I'll handle the script.

450
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:51,620
Bye.

451
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:53,763
Hello, Puen. I'm Talay's friend.

452
00:34:53,763 --> 00:34:56,255
He's with me right now.

453
00:34:57,740 --> 00:35:00,490
I didn't want to say that.

454
00:35:00,490 --> 00:35:05,284
I did it because I love him so much.

455
00:35:05,284 --> 00:35:08,356
I don't want his career to be ruined because of me.

456
00:35:09,450 --> 00:35:11,320
But damn.

457
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:15,316
My heart is aching so damn much.

458
00:35:15,980 --> 00:35:17,770
Did you hear that?

459
00:35:17,770 --> 00:35:21,860
I just want you to know that my friend has always loved you.

460
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:24,590
I miss our time together.

461
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:26,900
Can we go back to that universe?

462
00:35:28,680 --> 00:35:31,400
You're too drunk.

463
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:34,123
I'm ending it here, Puen. Bye.

464
00:35:45,010 --> 00:35:46,810
Handle it well.

465
00:35:49,168 --> 00:35:51,552
Follow the script the management team prepared for you.

466
00:35:51,552 --> 00:35:54,572
Don't go off it. Got it?

467
00:36:00,460 --> 00:36:02,360
Hey!

468
00:36:03,056 --> 00:36:05,552
Hello, everyone.

469
00:36:05,552 --> 00:36:07,870
Hi.

470
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:13,164
I'm here to confirm that the man in the picture is me.

471
00:36:14,990 --> 00:36:19,210
Talay said it was just two friends playing.

472
00:36:19,210 --> 00:36:21,928
What would you say about this, Puen?

473
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:26,080
That's right. We were just playing.

474
00:36:33,370 --> 00:36:37,436
But my feelings for him are real.

475
00:36:39,277 --> 00:36:41,400
Whoa. So it's true?

476
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:45,810
So are you and Talay boyfriends?

477
00:36:45,810 --> 00:36:47,840
- Are you?
- Is that right?

478
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,190
- How long have you been together?
- Please answer the question.

479
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:52,090
Not yet.

480
00:36:52,830 --> 00:36:57,150
But he's the one I have good feelings for.

481
00:36:57,150 --> 00:37:00,584
And I want to learn about him for as long as I can.

482
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:07,640
Someone asked me before

483
00:37:07,640 --> 00:37:12,010
what I would choose between love and work.

484
00:37:12,927 --> 00:37:17,370
Ask me countless times and my answer will be the same.

485
00:37:17,370 --> 00:37:19,820
I choose love.

486
00:37:19,820 --> 00:37:23,280
Without work, I can survive.

487
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:27,480
Without him, I can't.

488
00:37:47,850 --> 00:37:50,500
What's that look on your face?

489
00:37:50,500 --> 00:37:54,540
Puen told everyone about you. You should be happy.

490
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:57,310
I'm happy. I'm happy, of course.

491
00:37:57,310 --> 00:38:00,730
But I'm afraid that his job has been impacted.

492
00:38:00,730 --> 00:38:03,630
Especially now that his movie is airing.

493
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:06,290
Don't worry just yet.

494
00:38:07,530 --> 00:38:10,280
Let me check the feedback on Twitter.

495
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:15,900
Shit!

496
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:17,563
My mom is messaging me.

497
00:38:17,563 --> 00:38:20,723
Telling me to go home immediately. She needs to talk to me.

498
00:38:21,450 --> 00:38:24,240
So she knows about this?

499
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:26,300
Will she say anything?

500
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:29,480
I've never told my family about this.

501
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:35,320
I'm sure it'll be fine. I'll go with you.

502
00:38:48,120 --> 00:38:51,892
Puen is right there sitting on my friend's couch.

503
00:38:52,817 --> 00:38:55,383
Gyo, calm down.

504
00:38:56,320 --> 00:39:00,010
Puen, what are you doing here?

505
00:39:00,010 --> 00:39:01,930
I told the press about you.

506
00:39:01,930 --> 00:39:04,470
I'm here to take responsibility for my action.

507
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:09,212
Mom, I'm taking this chance to ask for your permission.

508
00:39:10,810 --> 00:39:12,003
Wait.

509
00:39:12,003 --> 00:39:14,221
What are you asking?

510
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:19,476
Asking if I could...

511
00:39:20,610 --> 00:39:22,652
take you out of town.

512
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:26,000
Can I, Mom?

513
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:27,450
Of course, you can.

514
00:39:27,450 --> 00:39:31,440
You can take him out of town, out of the country, or out of the universe.

515
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:33,500
I don't mind.

516
00:39:33,500 --> 00:39:36,120
Mom, aren't you worried about me at all?

517
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:39,332
How old are you, eight?

518
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:43,088
Your mom gave us permission.

519
00:39:43,088 --> 00:39:45,610
You can't say no.

520
00:39:45,610 --> 00:39:50,460
Someone like you would just drag me with you even though I said no.

521
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:54,670
Puen, you're welcome to eat here whenever you want.

522
00:39:54,670 --> 00:39:57,200
Just let Talay know.

523
00:39:57,200 --> 00:39:58,800
Thank you, Mom.

524
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:02,160
I guess I'll stop by to eat here quite often.

525
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:03,400
Sure.

526
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:05,320
Can I come, too?

527
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:09,980
I'm so overjoyed seeing these two together.

528
00:40:09,980 --> 00:40:11,580
Girl.

529
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:15,600
What a shame I didn't prepare anything today.

530
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:18,304
You won't get to try my recipe today.

531
00:40:18,304 --> 00:40:22,570
Can I borrow your kitchen for a day then?

532
00:40:22,570 --> 00:40:24,220
Yes.

533
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:28,720
And can I borrow Talay for a moment?

534
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:31,050
Take him.

535
00:40:31,050 --> 00:40:33,152
What are you doing?

536
00:40:33,152 --> 00:40:34,970
Cook.

537
00:40:34,970 --> 00:40:36,970
Let's go.

538
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:41,230
Your son is stubborn.

539
00:40:41,230 --> 00:40:43,030
Go.

540
00:40:45,310 --> 00:40:47,360
Cooking time.

541
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:50,344
What should we make here?

542
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,100
Talay,

543
00:40:59,100 --> 00:41:00,780
do you want this?

544
00:41:00,780 --> 00:41:04,756
Good idea. I want to eat Chef Puen's food.

545
00:41:14,447 --> 00:41:15,610
Hurry up. I'm hungry.

546
00:41:15,610 --> 00:41:17,163
Here. Eat it now.

547
00:41:17,163 --> 00:41:19,359
It's still hot.

548
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:25,956
Here you go.

549
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:32,640
I'll eat now.

550
00:41:45,408 --> 00:41:47,108
Do you want some?

551
00:41:55,456 --> 00:41:57,456
With egg whites.

552
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:02,868
Full bite.

553
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:05,520
Is it good?

554
00:42:08,700 --> 00:42:12,550
You helped me cook. That's why it's so good.

555
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:29,132
Phi Puen, can you feed Talay, please?

556
00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:35,050
It's messy.

